text: Joe Biden called Black youth super predators.
Joe Biden used the term super predators to refer to young Black men
A viral Facebook post shared over 700 times claims Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden called black people super predators in 1994.
While speaking of the Violent Crime Control and Law Enforcement Act of 1994, Joe Biden referred to Black Americans as super-predators.
